pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `canbo` ( `MACANBO` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MANHANKHAUTHUONGTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TENTAIKHOAN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MATKHAU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `LOAICANBO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MACANBO`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `hocsinhsinhvien` ( `MAHSSV` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TRUONG` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `DIACHITHUONGTRU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `THOIGIANBATDAUTAMTRUTHUONGTRU` date NOT NULL, `THOIGIANKETTHUCTAMTRUTHUONGTRU` date NOT NULL, `VIPHAM` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, PRIMARY KEY (`MAHSSV`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `nhankhau` ( `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `HOTEN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TENKHAC` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `NGAYSINH` date NOT NULL, `GIOITINH` varchar(10) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NOISINH` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGUYENQUAN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `DANTOC` varchar(20) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TONGIAO` varchar(20) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `QUOCTICH` varchar(20) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `HOCHIEU` varchar(20) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `NOITHUONGTRU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `DIACHIHIENNAY` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `SDT` char(10) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `TRINHDOHOCVAN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `TRINHDOCHUYENMON` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `BIETTIENGDANTOC` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `TRINHDONGOAINGU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `NGHENGHIEP` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MADINHDANH`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `nhankhautamtru` ( `MANHANKHAUTAMTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NOITAMTRU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TUNGAY` date NOT NULL, `DENNGAY` date NOT NULL, `LYDO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `SOSOTAMTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MANHANKHAUTAMTRU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `nhankhautamvang` ( `MANHANKHAUTAMVANG` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGAYBATDAUTAMVANG` date NOT NULL, `NGAYKETTHUCTAMVANG` date NOT NULL, `LYDO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NOIDEN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MANHANKHAUTAMVANG`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `nhankhauthuongtru` ( `MANHANKHAUTHUONGTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `DIACHITHUONGTRU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `QUANHEVOICHUHO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci, `SOSOHOKHAU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MANHANKHAUTHUONGTRU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;
CREATE TABLE `quanhuyen` ( `maqh` varchar(5) NOT NULL, `ten` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `kieu` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `matp` varchar(5) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`maqh`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `sohokhau` ( `SOSOHOKHAU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MACHUHO` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `DIACHI` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGAYCAP` date NOT NULL, `SODANGKY` char(7) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`SOSOHOKHAU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `sotamtru` ( `SOSOTAMTRU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `CHUHO` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NOITAMTRU` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGAYCAP` date NOT NULL, `DENNGAY` date NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`SOSOTAMTRU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tienantiensu` ( `MATIENANTIENSU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `TOIDANH` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `HINHPHAT` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `BANAN` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGAYPHAT` date NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MATIENANTIENSU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tieusu` ( `MATIEUSU` char(9) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MADINHDANH` char(12) COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `THOIGIANBATDAU` date NOT NULL, `THOIGIANKETTHUC` date NOT NULL, `CHOO` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NGHENGHIEP` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `NOILAMVIEC` text COLLATE utf32_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MATIEUSU`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf32 COLLATE=utf32_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `xaphuongthitran` ( `maxp` varchar(5) NOT NULL, `ten` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `kieu` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `maqh` varchar(5) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`maxp`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
